    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081510/extras/3772d07c61cd427eff75b7e3293ac05a.poster.avif?t=1765903394\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081510/extras/3772d07c61cd427eff75b7e3293ac05a.webm?t=1765903394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>关于《青蛙帮》</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>加入银河系最强青蛙帮派！</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081510/extras/458f3e83ce36a5ceeaa01f7695d7306f.poster.avif?t=1765903394\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081510/extras/458f3e83ce36a5ceeaa01f7695d7306f.webm?t=1765903394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>化身无畏蛙匪，率领你的“青蛙帮”，驰骋于狂野的浩瀚宇宙。击退成群怪物，探访奇诡文明，发掘埋藏在远古遗迹中的无价宝藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>独自冒险，或与友并肩作战！</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081510/extras/100a6e37b1f606d91e48306efe4fde85.poster.avif?t=1765903394\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081510/extras/100a6e37b1f606d91e48306efe4fde85.webm?t=1765903394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>是组队出击，还是单枪匹马？在危机四伏又惊喜连连的手工打造世界中，按你的方式探索银河！每个角色都身怀绝技，让每一场战斗都混乱炫酷！驾驶你忠实的帆船，在各个任务间灵活跳跃，轰杀如潮水般涌来的敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>狂轰 – 夺宝  – 变强</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081510/extras/606e5457faef5d5876a5fbe46d44ec11.poster.avif?t=1765903394\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081510/extras/606e5457faef5d5876a5fbe46d44ec11.webm?t=1765903394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>《青蛙帮》融合了流畅爽快的战斗与深度的进度系统。利用强大的战利品装备你的青蛙团队，解锁技能并升级装备，最终成为银河中最强大、最令人敬畏的青蛙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>准备好征服星河了吗？</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081510/extras/fd4adea700496e428fc202b586d3e8eb.avif?t=1765903394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081510/extras_big/fd4adea700496e428fc202b586d3e8eb.avif?t=1765903394 width=800 height=352 /></span></p>",
